    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good, reliable condition and has been well-maintained by its previous owner. The exterior paint retains a nice shine, though you may find a few minor surface scratches and a small door ding if you look closely. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the seats are in great shape with no rips or tears, and all power features are fully functional. Mechanically, it drives smoothly with no known issues, and the service records indicate regular oil changes and inspections. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car ready for its next owner.",
