    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for. The exterior paint retains a strong gloss with only a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, barely noticeable scratch on the rear passenger door. Inside, the cabin is clean and smoke-free; the upholstery is in great shape, though there is some light wear on the driver\u2019s seat bolster consistent with careful use. All electronic features, including the infotainment system and climate control, are fully functional. Mechanically, the car is solid, featuring a consistent service history and a recently completed inspection. The engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts crisply, and the tires have plenty of tread remaining. This is a reliable, attractive vehicle that is ready for the road with no immediate maintenance required.",
      "price": 34500.0,
