      "description": "Hey there! You've got to see this absolute beauty. It\u2019s honestly in pristine condition\u2014looks and feels just like it rolled off the showroom floor yesterday! I\u2019ve taken such good care of it, always garage-kept and treated like my baby. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new without the factory price tag, this is the one for you. Come take it for a spin and fall in love!",
