      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This collector-grade E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 power plant features a robust 8,000 RPM redline with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS timing, delivering linear power across the entire rev range. This specimen has undergone preventative rod bearing replacement and comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement to ensure structural integrity under high lateral loads. The ZF 6-speed manual transmission engages with crisp, mechanical precision, paired with a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. Every bushing, seal, and suspension component is in peak operating condition,",
